<p>refused to wear it, so along came our own.</p>
<p>8th. This is our daily routine, Physical jerks from 6. till 6.30 parade from 9 till 11.30, parade again in the afternoon from 2 till 4, &amp; then again in the evening  All N.C.O's have to attend Instruction classes on the Lewis Gun. so you can see they keep us going</p>
<p>This morning in addition to our usual drill the whole Company had to go through a bomb course &amp; each man had to sling 2 bombs about 20 yards, there was only 1 dud in about 70, so the bombs were pretty good &amp; reliable Mills" were the bombs used</p>
